# decomp/mods/transplant/manifest
#
# Per-function override manifest for the transplant mod.
#
# Format: <function_symbol>  <override_file_path>
# Override paths are relative to this manifest's directory.
#
# The splice toolchain reads this file, groups overrides by their
# pristine TU, and emits one spliced TU per modded TU under
# build/transplant/race/spliced/. The unity-build pipeline then
# consumes the spliced TUs in the same source-order slot the
# pristine TU would have occupied.
#
# Currently empty -- entries land here as we migrate transplant
# overlays from mods/transplant/race/*.s into per-function .c
# overrides under decomp/mods/transplant/race/.
